videos.description: Lonzo Ball throws up a lob at an awkward angle on the fast break, but Jaxson Hayes is able to grab the pass and somehow make the layup for the Pelicans.

videos.description: Lonzo Ball heats up early against the Suns as he knocks down four 3-pointers in the first half as the Pelicans establish a 66-59 halftime lead.
